"addition to the gas fees needed to deploy the contract on the blockchain, "
"which is not returned. We ``assert`` that the deposit is divisible by 2 to "
"ensure that the seller deposited a valid amount. The constructor stores the "
"item's value in the contract variable ``self.value`` and saves the contract "
"creator into ``self.seller``. The contract variable ``self.unlocked`` is "
